trans-unit.source: Enables a non-control component to emulate the data-binding behavior of a Windows Forms control.
trans-unit.target: Fa in modo che un componente diverso da un componente di controllo simuli il comportamento di associazione dati di un controllo Windows Form.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> contains a reference to its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.IBindableComponent> owner through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.BindableComponent%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> contiene un riferimento relativo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.IBindableComponent> proprietario mediante il <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.BindableComponent%2A> proprietà.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control> class implements this interface, so if your bindable component inherits from <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control>, you do not need to implement this interface.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control> implementa questa interfaccia, pertanto se il componente associabile eredita da <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control>, non è necessario implementare questa interfaccia.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the collection of currency managers for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.IBindableComponent" />.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta l'insieme di gestori della valuta per l'interfaccia <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.IBindableComponent" />.

trans-unit.source: The collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingManagerBase" /> objects for this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.IBindableComponent" />.
trans-unit.target: Raccolta di oggetti <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingManagerBase" /> per questa interfaccia <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.IBindableComponent" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of data-binding objects for this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.IBindableComponent" />.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene l'insieme di oggetti di associazione dati per questa interfaccia <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.IBindableComponent" />.
